Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:43.42,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I walked ten thousand miles,ten thousands miles to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:50.19,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And every gasp of breath,I grabbed it just to find you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.49,0:00:58.25,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And every single step of the way,I paid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:10.39,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every single night and day I searched for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:22.25,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Through sand storms and hazy dawns I reached for you
